videos.description: Kendal Yancy gets through the West Virginia defense to get the layup and drawing the foul.
videos.headline: Kendal Yancy muscles his way to the rim

videos.description: Tarik Phillip finds an open Sagaba Konate. Konate slams it down.
videos.headline: Sagaba Konate posterizes Longhorn defender

videos.description: Jarrett Allen going to the rim hard with a slam dunk.
